column2:
"T-that's great!
You can defeat Garongo really
easily even with its thick armor!"

"That felt so epic!
This is how an active duty
ARKS fights!"

"<%me>...!
Could I call you Professor
from now on?!"

"I'd like to learn as much as I can
from you from now own until I become
a full-fledged ARKS!"
"Thank you so very much for all of your teachings! I look forward to learning more from you!"
